title: It Came from Planet Earth
description: Coming to you from Chapek 9. Humans will never come to their defenseless town. Or so they thought…
quote: I will eat and digest you all with my system of mighty organs!
altHero: a robot in a human costume with sharp teeth emerges from some bushes
alt1: two frightened robot teens in a parked car
alt2: the human’s open mouth reveals the robot actor inside
alt3: the robot opens its chest compartment to showcase human organs wired together
alt4: a robot General pokes the dead human with a stick
